WEBVTT

00:05.687 --> 00:08.090
So Jason comes home and tells us

00:08.090 --> 00:11.693
that he is joining the
debate team at school.

00:11.693 --> 00:13.061
We're thrilled.

00:13.062 --> 00:14.362
What better use

00:14.363 --> 00:16.598
of his naturally
argumentative nature, right?

00:16.599 --> 00:17.599
Mmm.

00:17.600 --> 00:19.134
Then...

00:19.135 --> 00:20.969
then he leaves the room,

00:20.970 --> 00:22.771
and Henry turns to me and says,

00:22.772 --> 00:26.074
“Do we really want him
getting better at it?”

00:27.944 --> 00:30.645
I'm sorry, I'm talking
too much about my kids.

00:30.646 --> 00:32.981
Oh, no, because you can't talk
about work, it's understood.

00:32.982 --> 00:35.684
Oh, I can... everybody is.

00:35.685 --> 00:37.719
Ah, you're going before the
House Appropriations Committee

00:37.720 --> 00:39.120
this week, huh?

00:39.121 --> 00:40.430
To defend my budget.

00:40.431 --> 00:43.024
Oh, squaring off with
Chairman Everard Burke.

00:43.025 --> 00:46.127
Mmm, affectionately known on
the Hill as Burke the Ripper.

00:46.128 --> 00:49.998
Every single one of our
outreach programs is under fire.

00:49.999 --> 00:52.634
It's gonna take some fancy footwork.

00:52.635 --> 00:55.103
You'll be fine... you got very fancy feet.

00:55.104 --> 00:57.672
Fancy shoes.

00:57.673 --> 01:00.433
And how's everything else?

01:01.442 --> 01:03.845
Guys, I mean it, how's everything else?

01:03.846 --> 01:04.470
It's fine.

01:04.471 --> 01:06.247
It's great. Thank you
for cooking, by the way.

01:06.248 --> 01:08.024
- Yeah.
- It's a really big treat.

01:08.025 --> 01:08.950
No problem.

01:08.951 --> 01:10.218
I realize it's the only way

01:10.219 --> 01:12.253
to keep spy reunion going.

01:12.254 --> 01:13.821
You and Isabelle don't want to be seen

01:13.822 --> 01:15.688
palling around D.C. hotspots.

01:15.689 --> 01:17.558
Not while you're
investigating Marsh's death.

01:17.559 --> 01:18.893
We're not investigating anything.

01:18.894 --> 01:20.228
- We just can't cook.
- Got it.

01:20.229 --> 01:21.662
All right, let's eat.

01:21.663 --> 01:23.064
Let's.

01:24.032 --> 01:26.466
Ooh, ow.

01:27.034 --> 01:28.903
- Bear up the bum.
- Aw...

01:28.904 --> 01:30.371
- I'm sorry.
- Very sweet.

01:30.372 --> 01:32.006
I didn't do the toy sweep.

01:32.007 --> 01:33.908
Mmm, too bad we couldn't see the kids.

01:33.909 --> 01:36.176
Are they with their dad tonight?

01:38.079 --> 01:40.081
They are.

01:40.082 --> 01:41.782
All week.

01:41.783 --> 01:43.751
Every week.

01:43.752 --> 01:44.752
What?

01:44.753 --> 01:47.355
I just lost custody.

01:47.356 --> 01:48.823
Wha... how?

01:48.824 --> 01:49.824
What?

01:49.825 --> 01:50.791
Why?

01:50.792 --> 01:52.960
The judge decided

01:52.961 --> 01:57.331
that I have a demanding
and high-risk occupation.

01:57.332 --> 01:58.999
- Oh.
- They're better off with their father,

01:59.000 --> 02:00.401
- a banker.
- Come on.

02:00.402 --> 02:01.678
He literally has banker's hours.

02:01.679 --> 02:03.003
Oh, that's outrageous.

02:03.004 --> 02:05.673
Come on, there has to
be some kind of recourse?

02:07.042 --> 02:08.508
I'll keep fighting it.

02:08.509 --> 02:10.477
It's just gonna drag on forever.

02:10.478 --> 02:11.845
I'm so sorry.

02:11.846 --> 02:13.047
Is there anything we can do?

02:13.048 --> 02:15.082
You know a guy with a baseball bat?

02:15.083 --> 02:17.516
Several, in fact.

02:19.086 --> 02:21.054
Out of the three of us,

02:21.055 --> 02:24.224
it's not like it was a
big competition for me.

02:24.225 --> 02:25.659
- Good-bye.
- I love you.

02:25.660 --> 02:26.693
You're always welcome.

02:26.694 --> 02:27.694
Thank you.

02:27.695 --> 02:28.695
Bye.

02:31.332 --> 02:32.366
That was rough.

02:32.367 --> 02:34.268
That was rough.

02:34.269 --> 02:35.802
- Poor Juliet.
- Mmm.

02:35.803 --> 02:38.205
What's going on with the Marsh case?

02:38.206 --> 02:40.274
Have you brought the CIA in yet?

02:40.275 --> 02:41.908
Munsey's on it.

02:41.909 --> 02:43.277
I'll keep in touch.

02:43.278 --> 02:45.311
- Love you.
- Love you.

